column1: 1927 Jan Gauge lowered from 4ft above ground to 1ft
1940 Aug has a dash on sheet, but as same in other parts of IOW given a zero
1956 Sept Advised by Mrs Newnham that golf course no longer exists. Gauge moved to private house
1956 Gauge moved to private house. Not stated, but in 1939 she was living in the Old Coastguard House, about 150yds NE
Altitude changed quite drastically from 250-340ft but none as marked as being trusted
